","floor":"#12-2","id":"1469506","time":"2019-7-26 21:47","userId":"aonoiris","userName":"松岛芷泺","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">好好</span> 说: 这里最打动好好的是“我的爱川流不息”，这种绵绵的感觉很真切，相比而言“穿越天际”就显得突兀苍白甚至还有点俗气的感觉~ </q></div>好好去听了呀，谢谢你吃我安利！！"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/73/407378.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1468688","time":"2019-7-25 08:54","userId":"harukizzp","userName":"加藤全栈","userSign":"(这个世界并不真实，现在让全部的光都归零。 ... ... ... ...)","message":"我高中写过，还发表过校刊，不知道还能不能翻出来，好几年前的事情了","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/15/31568.jpg","floor":"#13-1","id":"1468730","time":"2019-7-25 11:13","userId":"haohao69","userName":"好好","userSign":"","message":"WOW~很厉害的感觉呢~如果找到就放出来吧~"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/71/227195.jpg","floor":"#14","id":"1469002","time":"2019-7-25 23:39","userId":"227195","userName":"thofoofintwsi","userSign":"","message":"关于心中的话，<br>只对你一个人说<br>你是我生命中的精灵<br>你知道我所有的心情<br>是你将我从梦中叫醒<br>再一次给我开放的心灵","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/64/16437.jpg","floor":"#15","id":"1469003","time":"2019-7-25 23:40","userId":"sat","userName":"Sat","userSign":"(bababadalgharaghtakamminarronnkonnbronntonnerronnt ...)","message":"<a href=\"https://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNTE3MDM2OTY=.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">J'te L'dis Quand Même</a>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/44/14488.jpg","floor":"#16","id":"1469096","time":"2019-7-26 08:34","userId":"sengohanabi","userName":"線香花火","userSign":"(Say A Little Prayer)","message":"没对象，不写<br><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">越写越心酸</span>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/74/37469.jpg","floor":"#17","id":"1469104","time":"2019-7-26 09:06","userId":"fantasy","userName":"fantasy","userSign":"(Q, Σ, Γ, δ, q0, Z0, F)","message":"嗯。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/73/347384.jpg","floor":"#18","id":"1469733","time":"2019-7-27 14:21","userI